summary: This is an email chain from January 2020 regarding the service of subpoenas to multiple airlines and Expedia for travel records related to Ghislaine Maxwell. It shows an active investigation into Maxwell's travel patterns.

persons.name: Maurene
persons.context: Appears to be coordinating the service of subpoenas to airlines and Expedia for travel records related to Ghislaine Maxwell.

events.title: Subpoena Service Coordination
events.description: Email correspondence about serving subpoenas to United, Delta, Southwest, American, Airline Reporting Corp, and Expedia for travel records related to Ghislaine Maxwell.

locations: 28 Liberty Street, New York County (Manhattan), New York, New York 10005
keyFacts: Subpoenas were served to United, Delta, Southwest, American, and Airline Reporting Corp for travel records.
A subpoena was being prepared for service to Expedia specifically for 'Maxwell travel' records.
Expedia's legal process was handled by National Registered Agents, Inc./CT Corp System at 28 Liberty Street in Manhattan.
